title: Comfortable and Historic 2-bedroom apartment coming available!
posting_body: This spacious historic 2-Bedroom apartment is located in Tremont, one of Cleveland's oldest neighborhoods.
Pre-leasing now for a July move-in time frame!
At Chelsea Manor our historic building offers high ceilings, and gorgeous woodwork.
This apartment is located on the fourth floor of the building, and features hard surface flooring throughout, and is walking distance to award winning restaurants, pubs, coffee shops and MUCH MORE!
* Pet Friendly community, with some restrictions!
* Professionally owned and managed with uniformed maintenance staff
* Close to downtown, Ohio City, I-90 and shopping at Steelyard Commons!
* Rent includes heat, water/ sewer, trash, and FREE off street parking in our PRIVATE lot!
